Are you all not afraid of death?

1093
01:29:06.667 --> 01:29:08.059
The Chinese are not afraid of death!

1094
01:29:08.083 --> 01:29:09.768
- That's right!
- The Chinese are not afraid of death!

1095
01:29:09.792 --> 01:29:12.309
- The Chinese are not afraid of death!
- The Chinese are not afraid of death!

1096
01:29:12.333 --> 01:29:13.333
Okay.

1097
